                "caption": "Figure 2:Overview of the SciIR-82k pipeline grounded in Peirce’s Semiotic Triad[29].The framework comprises three stages: (1) Corpus Construction, employing YOLO11 and InternVL 3.5 for sub-figure extraction and filtering; (2) Semiotic Stratification, categorizing samples into Icon, Index, and Symbol tracks; and (3) Reasoning-Driven Annotation, which leverages Qwen3 models to reverse-engineer Sci-RCoT and prompts.",
